# Reviews API
```shell
curl "http://api.bestbuy.com/v1/reviews(submissionTime%3E2015-04-29&sku=3142553)?pageSize=2&format=json&apiKey=YourAPIKey"
```
```javascript
var bby = require('bestbuy')('YourAPIKey');
bby.reviews('submissionTime>2015-04-29&sku=3142553',{pageSize:2}).then(function(data){
  console.log(require('util').inspect(data, false, null));
});
```

