The Reviews API provides access to individual consumer reviews that have been submitted on **BESTBUY.COM** for the products we sell. You can use it to retrieve information such as the author of the review, the date that the review was submitted, the reviewer's rating (0-5 where 5 is the best) of a product and the reviewer's comments about the product.

Both real-time calls and bulk download calls are available for Reviews data. These are updated daily.

The Reviews data include the review ID, author info, reviewer rating for a product, comments submitted and the time of submission for each review.

### Common Attributes

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
**comment** | Comment left by the reviewer
**id** | A unique review identifier for each review submitted
**rating** | Average "score" or ratings as submitted by reviewers. The rating attribute provides an average of all the ratings submitted for a product by reviewers. The ratings that can be submitted using a range from zero to five where five is the best rating that can be given. Ratings may be returned using decimals (example 3.5)
**reviewer** | The "nickname" of the reviewer submitting the review
**sku** | SKU identifier for a product
**submissionTime** | The date and time the review was submitted
**title** | The title of the review given by the reviewer
